formulas(assumptions).

%We present a series of formula showing the effects of constraint propagation for each pair of FOL constraint/RA operator
%Starting with the propagation of a guard over Y after a join

%We have Y = cond in R1 and we see that its also hold in R 

%CONSTRAINT A
%Guard
all y all z (R1(y,z) -> y = cond).

%MAPPINGS A TO B
all x all y all z (R(x,y,z) <-> R1(y,z) & R2(x,y)).

end_of_list.

formulas(goals).

all x all y all z (R(x,y,z) -> y = cond).

end_of_list.

